Privacy Policy:

At [שנ"צ בתחב"צ], we are dedicated to safeguarding your privacy and maintaining the confidentiality of your personal information. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, utilize, and disclose the information obtained through the use of our app, [שנ"צ בתחב"צ], designed to provide a location-based alarm clock experience for public transport users. This policy applies to the version available on the App Store and Play Store.

1. Information Collection and Use:
   1.1 Personal Information: We do not collect any personally identifiable information (PII) without your explicit consent. We understand the importance of privacy and strive to minimize the collection of personal data.
   1.2 Location Information: To offer the core functionality of our app, we require "always allow" permission to access your device's GPS location. This data is solely used to determine your location in order to set location-based alarms and wake you up as you approach your destination. We do not store your precise location data beyond the immediate use within the app.
   1.3 Notifications: We request permission to send notifications to your device for the purpose of delivering alarm alerts and other relevant information related to your app usage. We do not use notifications for any other purpose.
   1.4 Usage Data: We may collect non-personal information about your usage of the app, including app settings, preferences, and interactions. This data is utilized to improve the app's functionality, optimize user experience, and analyze app performance. It does not identify you personally.

2. Data Sharing and Disclosure:
   2.1 Third Parties: We do not share or disclose personal information or location data collected through the app with any third parties unless required by law or with your explicit consent.
   2.2 Aggregated Data: We may generate aggregated, non-personal data to analyze app usage patterns, identify trends, and improve our services. This aggregated data does not contain any personally identifiable information and cannot be used to trace back to individual users.
   2.3 Security: We employ industry-standard security measures to protect your personal information against unauthorized access, disclosure, or alteration. However, please be aware that no method of data transmission over the internet or electronic storage is entirely secure.

3. Children's Privacy:
   Our app is not intended for use by individuals under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children. If we discover that a child under 13 has provided us with personal information, we will take immediate steps to remove such data from our servers.

4. Updates to the Privacy Policy:
   We reserve the right to update this Privacy Policy periodically to reflect any changes to our data practices. We recommend reviewing the Privacy Policy within the app regularly to stay informed about our procedures and any updates.

5. Contact Us:
   If you have any questions, concerns, or requests regarding your privacy and the app, please don't hesitate to contact us at [contact email]. We will make every effort to respond to your inquiries promptly.

By using [שנ"צ בתחב"צ], you signify your agreement to the terms and conditions outlined in this Privacy Policy.

Please note that this is a general template tailored to your app's specific requirements. You may need to further customize the policy to address any additional features or unique aspects of your app.
